>> title: Spaghetti Carbonara
>> servings: 2
>> changelog: Bumped pecorino to 60g; richer.

Bring a pot of salted water to the boil and add @spaghetti{200%g}.

Whisk together @egg yolks{4} with @pecorino{60%g} grated.

Render @guanciale{120%g} in a cold pan until crisp.

Combine pasta, fat, and egg mixture off the heat. Season with @black pepper{}.
